data.description: This Antelope Valley ranch is a horse lovers dream with privacy, extensive facilities and a 1800 sq.ft. home, all within 30 minutes of downtown Reno.    The 10 acre fenced property backs up to BLM land and includes 2 24 X 24 horse shelters with corrals, an open barn, exercise pen and enough corral panels to set up a 60 X 60 ft area, a tack shed and a 20 X10 separate garage/storage building.    The ranch house had new interior paint, carpets and plank vinyl flooring.     Don't miss this rare opportunity. Enjoy the views and serenity from the covered porch or the fenced front and rear yard. There is a fenced dog run accessible via the garage, full sized Samsung steam washer/dryer, new garage doors in 2021, tankless hot water system, and electric sub panel ready for a spa in the backyard. The kitchen has granite counters, gas stove and beautiful open space views from your breakfast nook.
